Load "amaldots.abk"

Screen Open 0,320,256,2,0
Flash Off : Curs Off : Hide : Cls 0 : Palette $43,$65
Double Buffer : Screen Hide 0
Synchro Off 
'
For A=1 To 63
   Bob A,-1,-1,1
   Channel A To Bob A
   A$="A0,(1,3)(2,3)(3,3)(4,3)(5,3)(6,3)(5,3)(4,3)(3,3)(2,3);"
   A$=A$+"L:LX=Z(160)+110;LY=Z(100)+60;MZ(600)-300,Z(1000)-500,Z(100)+50;JL"
   Amal A,A$ : Amal On A
   Synchro 
Next A
'
Screen Show 
'
Do 
   Synchro 
   Wait Vbl 
Loop 





